data.description: Remarks: Updated Pictures! All personal property gone and move-in ready! Views, privacy, and National Forest! What more could you ask for? This 3 bed, 2 bath home on 2.343 acres backs up to National Forest and is just out of town enough to afford privacy but close enough for a quick trip to town. The main level has a master bed and bath plus another bed and common bath. Washer and dryer located on the main level. The daylight, walkout basement has an additional bed plus a large living area and rooms for storage/pantry. Use the wood stove, propane fireplace, 2 ductless heat pumps or electric cadets for heat. Include a porch to view the mountains and a 2 car detached garage and you have it all!
